            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1607753787,
            "creation_date": 1607751576,
            "body": "<p>You can use DecimalFormat to overcome this problem.<\/p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>//Make a new instance df that has 2 decimal places pattern.\nDecimalformat df = new DecimalFormat(&quot;#.##&quot;);\n\n// converting maltRequired form double to string.\nString maltRequiredString  = df.format(maltRequired);\n\n// then set the value of maltRequiredString to the TextView.\nmaltRequiredTextView.setText(String.valueOf(maltRequiredString));\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
